topic.title: lost username in zeronet
topic.body: long time ago i tried zeronet with an username, then my pc broke and wasn't able to use it anymore, registered again with a new username, cause my old one was already taken (by me of course), no way i can get my old username back?

1557064345_1GqfwGz2U6QVTSE4LxuudaJcnap92.body:
> [z9eradct](#comment_9_1AKTv64HemAWmM762raYNn8aeDNAoojaMd): Do you have backup of data/users.json ? If you do and restore it, your old name should return.

of course not but thank you for pointing out, i will do a backup next time...
